# Pacientes API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@authToken = {{authToken}}

## Rutas publicas

### Crear paciente (publico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docType": "DNI",
  "docNumber": "12345678",
  "firstName": "Luis",
  "lastName": "Martinez",
  "birthDate": "1990-05-20",
  "gender": "M",
  "phone": "3001112222",
  "email": "luis@example.com",
  "address": "Calle 123",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar pacientes (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pacientes/public
Accept: application/json

### Obtener paciente por id (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/1/public
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar paciente (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/1/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "3009998888",
  "address": "Carrera 45 # 12-34",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar paciente fisicamente (publico)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/1/public

### Baja logica de paciente (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/1/logic/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

## Rutas protegidas (requieren token)

### Crear paciente (con auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docType": "CE",
  "docNumber": "987654321",
  "firstName": "Maria",
  "lastName": "Gomez",
  "birthDate": "1985-03-15",
  "gender": "F",
  "phone": "3015556666",
  "email": "maria.gomez@example.com",
  "address": "Avenida 10 # 20-30",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar pacientes (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pacientes
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtener paciente por id (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar paciente (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "3021112233",
  "address": "Calle 50 # 60-70",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar paciente fisicamente (con auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Baja logica de paciente (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/paciente/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}
